radius:10px;margin-bottom:12px;overflow:hidden\"><button style=\"width:100%;background:transparent;border:none;padding:18px 20px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;color:#e2e8f0;text-align:left\"><div><div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600\">What the 9-factor confluence means</div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin-top:3px\">Why nine indicators and how to read the score</div></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.3)\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div style=\"border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:10px;margin-bottom:12px;overflow:hidden\"><button style=\"width:100%;background:transparent;border:none;padding:18px 20px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;color:#e2e8f0;text-align:left\"><div><div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600\">How Take Profit and Stop Loss are calculated</div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin-top:3px\">ATR-based volatility-adjusted levels — not arbitrary percentages</div></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.3)\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div style=\"border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:10px;margin-bottom:12px;overflow:hidden\"><button style=\"width:100%;background:transparent;border:none;padding:18px 20px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;color:#e2e8f0;text-align:left\"><div><div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600\">Kelly Criterion position sizing</div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin-top:3px\">The math behind how much to risk on each trade</div></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.3)\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div style=\"border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:10px;margin-bottom:12px;overflow:hidden\"><button style=\"width:100%;background:transparent;border:none;padding:18px 20px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;color:#e2e8f0;text-align:left\"><div><div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600\">How the backtest works</div><div style=\"font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin-top:3px\">Walk-forward validation — what it means and why it matters</div></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.3)\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div style=\"margin-top:48px;padding:24px;background:rgba(255,68,102,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,68,102,0.15);border-radius:10px\"><div style=\"font-size:10px;color:#ff4466;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:8px\">IMPORTANT DISCLAIMER</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);line-height:1.8\">QuantSignal is an educational tool. All signals are generated by machine learning models and do not constitute financial advice. Past backtest performance does not guarantee future results. Always do your own research.</div></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_ne